divs: Sighting DetailsMy husband saw Green ligth, glow, apprear in sky, horizontal, from east to west, too fast, while we were at home, our windows were open and we can see the sky. It was less than one second. at 9 pm. We believe was a meteor, but the strange was color: glow green. Inmediatelly, we check twitter: the ligth was see also in Spain and Manhattan.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Caracas
